# self-join-same-table

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `join_transformation_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (join inner (eq ?col ?col) (scan ?t) (scan ?t))
rhs: (scan ?t)
